      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harlem"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "During the early 1900s, black families moved from downtown Manhattan to Harlem, seeking a more welcoming neighborhood.",
